high_descs: Turn right and take a step forward, then turn right again and walk up to the counter to the left of the oven.
Pick up the butter knife off of the counter in front of you.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right to face the counter.
Use the butter knife to slice the apple on the counter into three pieces.
Put the knife down on the loaf of bread that is on the counter.
Pick up one of the apple slices.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the oven.
Put the apple slice in the large metal pan that is on the front left burner of the stove.
Pick up the large metal pan with the apple slice in it.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then turn left again and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the large metal pan with the apple slice in it on the second shelf from the top, then close the fridge doors.
anns.task_desc: Put a large metal pan with an apple slice in it in the fridge.

high_descs: Move to stand in front of the counter directly to the left of the stove.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter.
Move a little closer to the edge of the counter while holding the knife.
Slice the small dinner roll that's behind the loaf of bread.
Place the knife on top of the loaf of bread that is not sliced.
Pick up a piece of roll that you just sliced.
Carry the roll to stand in front of the stove.
Place the roll in the pan on the front left burner, which is the one closest to you.
Pick up the pan with the roll in it.
Carry the pan with the roll in it to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the pan and roll on the second shelf.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan with a slice of roll in it to the fridge.

high_descs: Back up, turn right, turn right, cross room to the metal counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn left, turn right to face counter again.
Cut the apple on the counter into thirds.
Put knife on the plate on the counter.
Pick up one piece of the apple from the counter.
Go to the stove to the right of the counter and face it.
Put apple in the pot on the front left burner.
Pick up the pot from the stove.
TUrn left, turn left again, walk to the refrigerator.
Put the pot into the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put  a pot with a piece of apple in it in the refrigerator

high_descs: Turn around and head straight to the counter
Grab the knife off of the counter
Turn slightly to the left
Cut the apple into three slices
Place the knife onto the counter
Grab one of the apple slices
Turn right and stop at the oven
Put the apple in the bowl in the bottom left stove
Grab the bowl with the apple in it
Turn around and head to the fridge
Open the fridge and put the bowl in it
anns.task_desc: Putting a bowl with an apple in the fridge

high_descs: Move to the counter to the right side of the oven
Pick up the stainless knife sitting on top of the counter
Move to the same counter where you got the knife
Cut the apple behind the round brown item on the counter
Set the knife on top of the round brown item sitting on the counter
Pick up an apple slice on the counter
Carry the apple to the white oven
Place the cut apple in the silver square item on top of the stove
Pick up the silver square item with the apple in it
Carry the apple in the silver square item to the fridge
Open the fridge to place the silver square item with the apple in it on the shelf above the shelf with the egg, close the door
anns.task_desc: Place an apple slice in a square pan, place both in fridge

high_descs: Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the knife to the left of the spatula.
Take a half step to your left.
Cut the apple in front of you into three chunks with the knife.
Put the knife on the baked item on the counter in front of you.
Pick up a chunk of the apple.
Take a tiny step backwards then take a step to your right.
Put the chunk of apple in the pan on the front left burner.
Pick up the pan with the chunk of apple in it.
Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Put the pan in the fridge on the fifth shelf from the bottom on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan whit an apple in it in the fridge.
